These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: coffee, tea
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: december, september
The people have 2 different hobbies: board-games, chess
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: action, sports
1. the person watching action movies is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in september##8
2. the person who's birthday is in september is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is board-games##5
3. the person drinking coffee is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |
| Beverage      | tea     | coffee      |
| Birthday          | september | december    |
| Hobby         | chess   | board-games |
| Movie-Genre   | action  | sports      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, iced-tea
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: iris, begonia
The people have 2 different jobs:  librarian, software-developer
The people use 2 different means of transport: boat, snowmobile
1. the person drinking iced-tea is on the far right##1
2. the person who growsiris is somewhere to the left of the librarian##5
3. the software-developer is not to the right of the librarian##8
4. the person driving the boat is not the person who growsbegonia##6

.:: Answer ::.
|             |         1          |      2      |
| Beverage    | almond-milk        | iced-tea    |
| Flower       | iris         | begonia |
| Job         | software-developer | librarian   |
| Transport   | boat               | snowmobile  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-3::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: epic, thriller
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: folk, metal
The people use 2 different means of transport: car, bus
2 different pets are kept: cat, ferret
1. the person driving the car is in an odd position##4
2. the person driving the bus is not to the right of the owner of the ferret##8
3. the fan of folk is somewhere to the left of the person watching thriller movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |
| Movie-Genre   | epic       | thriller |
| Music-Genre   | folk       | metal    |
| Transport   | car | bus |
| Pet           | cat        | ferret   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-4::.
2 different pets are kept: hamster, goldfish
The people have 2 different jobs:  designer, nurse
There are 2 different nationalities: german, polish
The people use 2 different means of transport: airplane, tram
1. the german is somewhere to the right of the nurse##5
2. the owner of the hamster is not to the left of the person driving the tram##8
3. the person driving the tram is on the left of the owner of the hamster##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |
| Pet         | goldfish | hamster  |
| Job           | nurse  | designer |
| Nationality   | polish | german   |
| Transport     | tram   | airplane |

